log.content: Create a single index.html file containing a hello world. Include styling in a dark theme with bold and striking color choice.

This will create a file named `index.html` in the current directory with the specified content. The background of the page is set to a dark gray color (#2f2f2f), and the text is set to a bright green color (#00ff00). The header "Hello, World!" is set to a bright red color (#ff0000).
